DOW IN AUTOMOTIVE
The automotive industry is defined by constant evolution. Finding ways to help improve fuel economy and reduce emissions, while enabling improvements in safety and performance, are just some of the areas Dow works on every day. As populations grow, and economies around the globe develop and improve their transportation infrastructure, Dow technologies help the world move forward with enhanced functionality, safety and sustainability.









