Helping Manufacturers Grow and Be More Sustainable
Dow innovations are found in a wide variety of industrial settings, from pharmaceutical manufacturers to metalworking.






What can we help you find?





















Home


Markets and Solutions


Industrial










DOW BUSINESSES IN INDUSTRIAL
Discover the ways in which Dow innovations are having an impact on industrial manufacturers all over the world.











DOW POLYURETHANES


DOW COATING MATERIALS


DOW CORNING INDUSTRIAL






DOW INDUSTRIAL STORIES AND VIDEOS









 



VIDEO: The Science Inside Corrosion Protection

 

 



VIDEO: Industrial Solutions: Enabling Manufacturing

 

 



Dow Powerplay Revitalizing the Ice at a Classic Arena

 

 



ACCUTRACE™ helps government fight fuel tax evasion

 

 



VIDEO: Dow's environmentally-preferred additives keep paint fresh

 

 



VIDEO: Dow Microbial Control protects both a ship’s hull and the environment

 

 



VIDEO: Harnessing the Power of the Sun

 

 



The growing role of improved acrylics in industrial coatings (PDF)

 

 



FILMTEC™ ECO addresses the challenge of water scarcity

 

Show More











DOW IN INDUSTRIAL
Dow has helped in the manufacturing of the world’s goods and services with additive solutions that:

Minimize friction and heat in mechanical processes
Manage the oil and water interface
Deliver active ingredients for maximum effectiveness
Facilitate dissolvability
Enable product authentication

Dow has also developed innovative solutions for the sustainable use of solvents in high quality metal cleaning and dry cleaning applications. In addition, Dow has developed ingredients for cleaning products used in institutional environments.
Dow innovations have extended into the pharmaceutical industry with solutions that help in the manufacture of medicine.









 WE CREATE A WIDE RANGE OF INNOVATIVE AND SUSTAINABLE PRODUCTS FOR THE INDUSTRIAL MARKETS.








SEARCH PRODUCTS











