Our Roots Run Deep
Dow innovations help farmers feed the growing world.

PLAY VIDEO 






What can we help you find?





















Home


Markets and Solutions


Agriculture










DOW BUSINESSES IN AGRICULTURE
See how Dow is making a difference on farms around the world.












DOW AGROSCIENCES







DOW AGRICULTURE STORIES AND VIDEOS









 



Dow is helping to fight food insecurity in Africa

 

 



Isoclast™ is fighting plant pests in 22 countries

 

 



Chemicals are found everywhere – even in organic produce

 

 



Crop Defense Solutions let farmers to do more with fewer chemicals

 

 



Dow helps protect historic Midway Islands from invasive plants (PDF)

 

 



The Recipe for a Healthier World Begins with a Healthier Oil

 










DOW IN AGRICULTURE
Since the 1950s, Dow’s agricultural business has been discovering, developing and bringing sustainable solutions to market for the growing world. We are committed to helping farmers increase their crop productivity through higher yields, better varieties, and targeted weed, insect, and disease control. Our products and services balance the needs of boosting agricultural productivity while preserving the environment.









WE CREATE A WIDE RANGE OF INNOVATIVE AND SUSTAINABLE PRODUCTS FOR AGRICULTURE MARKETS.








