The Dow Chemical Co.





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: DOW
S&P 500 Component


Industry
Chemicals


Founded
1897


Founder
Herbert Henry Dow


Headquarters
Midland, Michigan, U.S



Area served

Worldwide



Key people

Andrew N. Liveris
(Chairman, President and CEO)


Products
Chemicals, plastics, performance chemicals, catalysts, coatings, crop technology, crude oil and natural gas exploration and production


Revenue

