DOW IN BUILDING & CONSTRUCTION
Today’s modern structures must be energy efficient, safe, durable and aesthetically pleasing. These simultaneous requirements call for unique technologies and innovations. At Dow, we understand that solutions to these challenges can come from anywhere. That’s why we look beyond traditional construction concepts to bring inspired ideas to building and construction projects of all kinds. From modest homes to monumental skyscrapers, Dow develops solutions to help insulate, protect and enhance.









WE CREATE A WIDE RANGE OF INNOVATIVE AND SUSTAINABLE PRODUCTS FOR BUILDING AND CONSTRUCTION MARKETS.








